OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FThe King hit the DJ decks to spin some
OL,7,Ftunes while on a visit to Manchester.
OL,9,FCharles met young people who have
OL,10,Freceived support from the King's Trust
OL,11,Fcharity as he toured Aviva Studios,
OL,12,Fhome of the city's arts organisation
OL,13,FFactory International.
OL,15,FAspiring DJ Christian St Louis, 22,
OL,16,Ffrom Middleton, Greater Manchester,
OL,17,Finvited the King to try his hand on
OL,18,Fthe mixing table.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
