PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FAs he put Charles through his paces,
OL,7,FMr St Louis explained: "First, you
OL,8,Fload up the tracks and then play this
OL,9,Fone ... there are so many buttons.
OL,10,FOnce you know what to do, it's easy."
OL,12,FThe King moved to the groove as an
OL,13,Fonlooker said: "It's not as easy as it
OL,14,Flooks, is it?"
OL,16,FCharles laughed and replied: "I'm
OL,17,Ftrying to get the hang of it."
OL,26,@oD@XOUrD@eO]uD@POUvD@NO]xD@^OUyD@^O]
