CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FMr St Louis, formerly from east
OL,7,FLondon, told the King that taking a
OL,8,FDJing course through the trust had
OL,9,Fbeen "more than helpful".
OL,11,FHe said: "I always wanted to DJ. Now I
OL,12,Fknow I can do it." He said he was
OL,13,Flooking for a job to save up and buy
OL,14,Fhis own decks, with a goal of bringing
OL,15,Fout his own EP music recording.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@XO]sD@JOUtD@RO]
