OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FIn 2024, the King's Trust joined
OL,7,Fforces with the Elba Hope Foundation,
OL,8,Fa public charity founded by actor
OL,9,FIdris Elba and his wife Sabrina to
OL,10,Flaunch Creative Futures, a range of
OL,11,Ffree courses designed to inspire young
OL,12,Fpeople through the arts, building
OL,13,Ftheir skills and confidence to work in
OL,14,Fthe creative industries.
OL,16,FElba was supported by the King's
OL,17,FTrust, formerly the Prince's Trust,
OL,18,Fwhen he was a teenager.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
