OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FAnother beneficiary from the King's
OL,7,FTrust, Mariama Gallow, 19, from
OL,8,FManchester, read her own poem to the
OL,9,FKing.
OL,11,FMs Gallow undertook a creative music
OL,12,Fcourse and went on to learn about
OL,13,Fhealth and social care.
OL,15,FCharles told her he had already seen
OL,16,Fan example of her poetry which Elba
OL,17,Fhad shown him on a piece of film.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
