PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FHe said: "It was fantastic. Really,
OL,7,Freally good."Charles also met young
OL,8,Fpeople who had learned skills in stage
OL,9,Fconstruction such as lighting, sound
OL,10,Fand production through the Factory
OL,11,FAcademy based at Aviva Studios.
OL,13,FCreative Futures has helped more than
OL,14,F100 young people across Manchester and
OL,15,Fis now supporting young people in
OL,16,Fother parts of the UK.
OL,26,@nD@JOUoD@MO]
