PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FLaunched in 2018 by Factory
OL,7,FInternational, the Factory Academy
OL,8,Faims to provide accessible career
OL,9,Fpathways into the creative industries
OL,10,Fand boost creative skills across the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FThe Factory Academy has collaborated
OL,14,Fwith the King's Trust to deliver
OL,15,Fprogrammes from Creative
OL,16,FFutures.Charles unveiled a plaque to
OL,17,Fmark his visit before he was treated
OL,18,Fto a performance outside by a choir
OL,19,Ffrom the Royal Northern College of
OL,20,FMusic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
