PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773753075
OL,3,CDJ Charles serves up royal remix
OL,4,Cduring visit to arts organisation
OL,6,FThe King spoke briefly to members of
OL,7,Fthe public who gathered outside the
OL,8,Fcity-centre venue including child-
OL,9,Fminder Jodie Pownall, from New Mills,
OL,10,FDerbyshire, who brought along one-year-
OL,11,Fold twins Teddy and Kuba, two-year-old
OL,12,FJackson, and Ronnie, Stevie and
OL,13,FGeorge, all aged one.
OL,15,FThey were rewarded for braving the
OL,16,Frain as Charles posed for a photograph.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
